  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> (the same as you would for pasta) and cook over a high heat for 10-15 min or until tender with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once done, add the <strong>chickpeas</strong> (no need to drain!) for a further 1 min until warmed through</p>\r\n<p>Once warmed through, drain and return everything to the pot</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
