        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the skin from the <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, removing all the white pith</p>\r\n<p>Cut the peeled <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into slices</p>\r\n<p>Cut each slice into rough pieces&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
