            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly</p>\r\n<p>Combine the&nbsp;<strong>apple cider</strong><strong>&nbsp;vinegar&nbsp;</strong>with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
