      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi sticks</strong> and cook on each side for 2-4 min or until golden</p>",
