    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>orange segments</strong>, <strong>chopped mint</strong>, <strong>rocket</strong> and the <strong>dressing</strong> to the <strong>cooked bulgur</strong></p>\r\n<p>Give everything a good mix up &ndash; this is your <strong>orange &amp; mint bulgur</strong></p>",
