      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> sesame seeds</strong>, <strong>sumac&nbsp;</strong>and&nbsp;<strong>oregano&nbsp;</strong>to a <strong>pestle &amp; mortar&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Grind to a fine powder &ndash; this is your<strong> za'atar</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
